## Quick Start

### 1. Install Python dependencies

Make sure you have Python 3.9 or newer, then:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Run the server

```bash
python app.py
```

You should see:

```
========================================================
  CipherChat Backend  —  http://localhost:5000
========================================================
```

### 3. Open the app

Visit **http://localhost:5000** in your browser.

