## Simulated Features

| Feature | Simulation method |
|---|---|
| QR entry | html5-qrcode CDN library reads camera |
| JWT token | Base64-encoded fake header.payload.signature |
| Multi-user chat | Backend generates random bot messages on request |
| Packet sniffer | 22 % base interception probability per message |
| DDoS attacks | 12 % chance per metrics tick; auto-recovers after 3–7 s |
| Session hijack | 7 % chance per session check; token auto-rotates |
| Geolocation | 8 preset "attacker" cities, random coordinate jitter |
| Security score | Formula: 100 − (intercept_ratio × 35) − (attacks × 1.5) |

